description: Proteomics on HCT116 cells. 3 samples wild-type, 3 samples Fbw7 KO. Subcellular fractionation to cytoplasmic and nuclear fractions. Proteins were reduced with DTT, alkylated with iodoacetamide, digested with trypsin, and labelled with TMT6-plex:  126,127,128 - wildtype; 129,130,131 - Fbw7 KO. Sample separation by high resolution isoelectric focusing at peptide level, whereafter 72 fractions were loaded onto reversed phase LC-MSMS
